{"build_type":"library","description":"Lowers a launch_worker_binary high instruction (worker-runtime-FINAL A5) into native low-ops. SLICE 1 (single child, tail-chain): allocate the child's per-instance region and stack, clone_thread the target worker binary with the region as its context (A8), bounded-poll the region for the child's delivered result, then write that result into the launcher's OWN context region slot 0 via the shared epilogue (A7 report-up). The launcher worker takes its own region as first param named context. cycle_type is read but inert for one child (tail-chain); multi-child + the three composition types are a later slice. Emits only const/call/clone_thread low-ops (mirrors lower-spawn-thread + lower-function-invocation forms).","module_name":"lower-launch-worker-binary-towards-native-operations","package_name":"lower-launch-worker-binary-towards-native-operations","function_definitions":{"lower-launch-worker-binary-towards-native-operations":{"return_type":"void","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"inst","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"ops","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_ct","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"cycle_type"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"extract-instruction-field-string-tolerating-empty","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"inst"},{"kind":"var","value":"k_ct"}],"result_assignment_variable":"ctv","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_operation":"string_equals","condition_target":"ctv","condition_value":"as-completed","branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"emit-as-completed-lowering-ops","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"inst"},{"k